, they asked the children to write a letter to Santa Claus listing all the things they wanted for Christmas. The kids listed big items like guitars, pianos, and toys\u2026 typical big presents that most children want at Christmastime.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Next, the children were asked to write a second letter\u2026 This time, to their parents. Same as the Santa letter, but this time they were asking what they would <\/span><b>want from their parents<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> for Christmas. And this is where the kids\u2019 answers got really interesting.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">For the most part, kids just want love, time and attention. They want you to be there for them, experience things with them, and play with them.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Presents are great. But<\/span><b> spending quality time with family is the most precious thing in the world.\u00a0<\/b><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Let\u2019s not forget that this weekend. :)<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Wishing you all a very Merry Christmas,<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Love, Joel<\/span><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Merry Christmas Eve, Friends! Before you set off on your fun-filled weekend of spoiling one another with presents and delicious meals\u2026 check out this video&#8230; <\/p>\n<p class=\"more\"><a class=\"more-link\" href=\"https:\/\/budgetsaresexy.vercel.app\/what-kids-really-want-for-christmas\/\">Read More<\/a><\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":28,"featured_media":64373,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"closed","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"footnotes":""},"categories":[62,197],"tags":[],"class_list":["post-63998","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-charity","category-family-finance"],"yoast_head":"<!-- This site is optimized 